      "content": "The masking is often achieved through sophisticated, layered obfuscation techniques that make the data appear as benign environmental telemetry. They don't send \"sadness level 8,\" but rather a complex string of correlated data points—like pacing frequency combined with ambient light decay—that only their proprietary servers can decode as an emotional state. This distributed, encrypted transmission makes it incredibly difficult for the average user to trace the specific mood payload back to a central, identifiable profile.",
